<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - OlympicY</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a6fa5, #166088);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        a {
            color: white;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        .logo {
            height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<div class="search-container" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <input type="text" placeholder="Cari materi..." id="404-search">
    <button onclick="searchFrom404()">Cari</button>
</div>
<script>
    function searchFrom404() {
        const query = document.getElementById('404-search').value;
        window.location.href = `/?search=${encodeURIComponent(query)}`;
    }
</script>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="assets/img/logo.png" alt="OlympicY Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Materi yang Anda cari tidak ditemukan. Mungkin sudah diluncurkan ke orbit lain ðŸš€</p>
        <a href="/">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
